column5: What would you guys say would be a fair price for a Garmin 240 blue fishfinder, Garmin 172 GPS (non-colour) with 2 bluchart chips for lake Erie and Huron. I tried looking on the net but because these models are a couple years old I can't get much of a price range.

AAAH Ebay  Prices in US and if you use Ebay and are registered check out completed sales. Garmin240 http://search.ebay.com/search/search.dll?c...&category0=  172  http://search.ebay.com/search/search.dll?c...&category0=
free! and ill make first offer
